<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Product Order Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #0056b3;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .details {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 10px;
            border-left: 5px solid #0056b3;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Product Order Request</h2>
        <p>Dear warehouse manager,</p>
        
        <p>This is a formal request from <strong>{{ agency_name }}</strong> to place an order for the following products:</p>
        
        <div class="details">
            <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> {{ order_id }}</p>
            <p><strong>Product List:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                {% for product in products %}
                    <li>{{ product.name }} - {{ product.quantity }} units</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
            <p><strong>Note : </strong> {{ note }}</p>
        </div>

        <p>We kindly request you to confirm the order and share any necessary details regarding delivery and payment.</p>

        <p>Looking forward to your response.</p>

        <p>Best Regards,<br>
        {{ agency_name }}<br>
        {{ agency_email }}
        {{ agency_Address }}<br>
        {{ agency_contact }}<br></p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email is generated automatically. If you have any questions, please contact {{ sender_email }}.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
